paying ransom?

11:09.702 --> 11:12.872 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KIRBY, U.S. Assistant
Secretary of State:
Well, I didn't say that it was
used -- that

11:12.906 --> 11:15.041 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
