11:57.951 --> 12:01.387 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we weren't quite sure that
the release
was going to happen.

12:01.421 --> 12:06.225 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we were worried about Iran
reneging on
that very lengthy negotiation
process that

12:06.259 --> 12:08.027 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
