13:18.297 --> 13:20.066 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
have military components.

13:20.099 --> 13:26.005 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And then there is a very strong
and strident
effort diplomatically to come to
a political

13:26.039 --> 13:27.940 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
solution inside Syria.

13:27.974 --> 13:32.078 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And right now, because the
cessation of hostilities
