himself, this isn't
about trust and it isn't about
blind faith.

13:58.638 --> 14:03.409 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
This will only work if Russia is
willing and
able to use the influence that
we know they

14:03.443 --> 14:08.481 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
