couple of
things there.

14:42.548 --> 14:48.488 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
First of all, the Russians have
had a long
relationship with and in Syria
for decades

14:48.521 --> 14:52.925 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
