Syrian people, and that's what
we're all working

15:34.500 --> 15:36.402 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
towards.

15:36.435 --> 15:40.339 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, we have said our policy is
that we don't
believe Bashar al-Assad, because
of his brutality,

15:40.373 --> 15:43.409 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
