future of Syria.

15:43.442 --> 15:44.410 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
We still believe that.

15:44.443 --> 15:45.745 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That is still the case.

15:45.778 --> 15:48.648 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Our view is, Assad cannot be at
the head of
such a government.

15:48.681 --> 15:52.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
